            <title>[FLINK-3304] AvroOutputFormat.setSchema() doesn&apos;t work in yarn-cluster mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3304</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Quoting flink cli (schema and names modified):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;The program finished with the following exception:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;User-defined object org.apache.flink.api.java.io.AvroOutputFormat@5f253dfb (org.apache.flink.api.java.io.AvroOutputFormat) contains non-serializable field userDefinedSchema = {&quot;type&quot;:&quot;record&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Pojo&quot;,&quot;namespace&quot;:&quot;com.example&quot;,&quot;fields&quot;:[&lt;/p&gt;
{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;id&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:[&quot;null&quot;,&quot;string&quot;],&quot;default&quot;:null,&quot;subtype&quot;:&quot;objectid&quot;}
